{"tid":468103,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ben Sir 亂入《誇世代》 教「頂你個肺」典故","createTime":"2017-11-14T05:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T05:54:26.000Z","uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c75a91bbfaf3f408335264dcced3420b140418f5","tid":468103,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"昨日播出的無綫劇《誇世代》中，竟出現Ben Sir教「粗口」環節！事緣歐陽震華（Bobby）飾演的宋仲基因墜機而與交通意外入院的吳業坤交換了靈魂，今集Bobby在醫院發現真相。Bobby望見藝人老婆田蕊妮在電視上玩到樂極忘形，即時嬲到講：「頂你個肺」洩憤，剛好被邵美琪聽到，繼而責罵，此時客串醫生一角的Ben sir就指出「頂你個肺」只是屬於粗口的邊緣，意思與粗口相近，但語氣比較輕。Ben sir更講起「頂你個肺」其實是源自「頂你個膽」一詞，典故是舊時有個女人為隱瞞自己曾經有性經驗，於新婚夜行房後，用墨水弄污床單扮處女。連劇集都可融入Ben sir的「粗口學堂」，Ben sir果然無處不在。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2zJe5JO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zJe5JO&d=UPjA6PuRRITyKL%2B8B9ZvRDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=06e65b49\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2zJe5JO</a>"},{"pid":"de5aaa13cf3abf72eb15ae555851c2722f4f605a","tid":468103,"uid":35014,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:51:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"48dd81a758a92aef79de46ea7636c557e6aee55c","tid":468103,"uid":582,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ben sir快d收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又開始唔抵得人紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84263e2ea375d5ed8090dd34dd240af5b03ac5d0","tid":468103,"uid":90890,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ben sir快d收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又開始唔抵得人紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔鐘意=唔抵得<br />\n又學到嘢"}]}